{"tid":1019403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每次去海洋公園都好憎太陸人","createTime":"2019-02-13T02:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T02:57:20.000Z","uid":118671,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55daa1fb355600c9f4ec7254ce45edcb9383d340","tid":1019403,"uid":118671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:24:16.000Z","msg":"仲記得細個去海洋公園既時候好開心，全場都大多數係香港人，雖然玩咩機動遊戲或者睇熊貓個D動物都要排隊，但因為大家都係香港人，所以都識排隊，唔會左攝右攝<br />\n但近呢幾年海洋公園唔再屬於香港人，係屬於大陸人架！<br />\n仆你個街你班死蝗蟲，連香港人童年回憶你都要拎埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家入親海洋公園玩，大多數都係蝗蟲，D蝗全部都無文化，唔撚識排隊，一見有位就左攝右攝迫埋黎，什至係你眼前打尖，搞到依家排隊個空間越黎越窄，呼吸都有困難，吊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你班蝗蟲不如學好排隊先入黎啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9313991f44609273d831c818a764a847780b1499","tid":1019403,"uid":98223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:24:46.000Z","msg":"太陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82190ca7276a344b619d201502af6ec2eb744fbd","tid":1019403,"uid":118671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9313991f44609273d831c818a764a847780b1499","tid":1019403,"uid":98223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:24:46.000Z","msg":"太陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:32:15.000Z","msg":"sorry打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408f079200b8b5f012d18fbfed28b1a07e94d465","tid":1019403,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"唔止海洋公園 成個香港都係"},{"pid":"f9e13bd80237e8e6f866cb24c2dd58fbaadaa01e","tid":1019403,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"82190ca7276a344b619d201502af6ec2eb744fbd","tid":1019403,"uid":118671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9313991f44609273d831c818a764a847780b1499","tid":1019403,"uid":98223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:24:46.000Z","msg":"太陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:32:15.000Z","msg":"sorry打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"唔係大陸 係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打返好個屌字先啦<br />\n吊起佢哋都無撚用㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家唔會去海洋公園同迪士尼嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}